OL,7,FA 29-year-old man who turned up at a
OL,8,Fmosque in Portsmouth wielding a knife
OL,9,Fafter attacking a group of men, women
OL,10,Fand children praying has been jailed
OL,11,Ffor 20 months.
OL,13,FCallum Mcinally had shouted verbal
OL,14,Fabuse at the group gathered outside
OL,15,Fthe Jami Mosque on Victoria Road
OL,16,Fbefore he punched a man who asked him
OL,17,Fto leave them alone.
