OL,4,Cshouting racist abuse at group at
OL,5,Cmosque
OL,7,FA CPS spokesman said: "The incident,
OL,8,Fwhich took place on 31 August at the
OL,9,FPortsmouth Jami Mosque, saw Mcinally
OL,10,Fshouting verbal abuse whilst he
OL,11,Fapproached a small group of men, women
OL,12,Fand children who were praying.
OL,14,F"After a man from the group asked
OL,15,FMcinally to leave them alone, Mcinally
OL,16,Fpunched him to the chest, kicked a
OL,17,Fprayer mat and shouted racial abuse.
OL,19,F"Mcinally later returned and pulled
OL,20,Fout a knife, which he discarded and
OL,21,Fran away once he heard police sirens."
