OL,7,FSenior crown prosecutor Harvey
OL,8,FWithecombe said: "We ensured that
OL,9,FCallum Mcinally appeared before the
OL,10,Fcourt straight away.
OL,12,F"The sentence handed today, after the
OL,13,FCrown Prosecution Service successfully
OL,14,Fapplied for a hate crime uplift,
OL,15,Fproves there is nowhere to hide for
OL,16,Fthose who are intent on spreading
OL,17,Fhate, malice and prejudice in our
OL,18,Fcommunities.
