OL,7,F"We will continue to act swiftly and
OL,8,Frobustly regarding these cases and
OL,9,Fensure those responsible for such
OL,10,Fcrimes in our communities are brought
OL,11,Fto justice."
OL,13,FChief Inspector Sam Warne, of
OL,14,FHampshire Constabulary, said: "I am
OL,15,Fglad to see the seriousness of this
OL,16,Fincident recognised in today's result.
OL,18,F"Mcinally's behaviour shocked the
OL,19,Fcommunity, and I hope his sentencing
OL,20,Fgoes someway to helping repair
OL,21,Fcohesion in our communities.
