OL,7,F"My officers and I are dedicated to
OL,8,Fmaking Portsmouth a safer place for
OL,9,Fall. Hate-related incidents such as
OL,10,Fthis will not be tolerated and anyone
OL,11,Ffound to commit such offences will be
OL,12,Fbrought to justice.
OL,14,F"I would like to thank the people of
OL,15,FPortsmouth for their support as we
OL,16,Fcontinue to work with our partners and
OL,17,Fcommunity leaders to strengthen our
OL,18,Fresponse, both in this and future
OL,19,Fincidents"
